desc: Miami South Dade online shop for live plants, flowers, stems, planters, vases, etc delivered to your door the next day.

layout.text: Shop Houseplants with Free delivery + replacement in South Dade
If you live in the South Dade area (south of Dadeland mall) take advantage of our free delivery either same day or next day. Plus if your plant dies within 30 days we'll replace it for free.
